title: Delta Of Venus
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Caribbean, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu is mostly vegetarian with vegan options. Daily brunch served until 2pm offering egg and vegan omelettes, granola, oatmeal. Lunch sandwiches, soup, and salads. Dinner main entrees including tofu, tempeh, and seitan dishes Caribbean style. Also vegan muffins, brownies, and cookies.
